# Release sync (URGENT)

When shipping or completing user-facing work in Word of the Day App, you **must** update these together in the **same session**:

1. **`app/build.gradle.kts`** — increment `versionCode`, set `versionName`
2. **`app/src/main/java/com/example/wordofday/data/release/AppReleaseCatalog.kt`** — add/update `AppRelease` row (modal bullets)
3. **`DOCS/CHANGELOG.md`** — cut version section from `[Unreleased]`
4. **`DOCS/EDITIONS_ROADMAP.md`** — edition status + checkboxes
5. **`DOCS/SCRATCHPAD.md`** — last actions

In-app What's New reads **`AppReleaseCatalog`** only. If catalog and CHANGELOG diverge, the update modal is wrong — **release blocker**.

Full protocol: **`AGENTS.md`** → "URGENT — Release sync protocol".
